<div class="row">
	<div class="md-12-col">
		<h1>Zcash <-> Eth Atomic Swap</h1>
		<p>
			Suppose Alice agees to trade ETH for ZEC with Bob.
		</p>
		<ol>
			<li>Alice and Bob set up a <a href="/wallet">HD wallet</a> for ZEC.</li>
			<li>Alice <a href="/trade/eth/init">creates</a> a hashlock contract on Ethereum.</li>
			<li>Bob <a href="/trade/zec/init?tradeId=1">reviews</a> the terms of ZEC contract and funds it.</li>
			<li>Alice <a href="/trade/zec/settle?tradeId=1">redeems</a> ZEC in P2SH by providing preimage.</li>
			<li>Bob redeems ETH by <a href="/trade/eth/settle?tradeId=1">unlocking</a> the contract with the preimage.</li>
		</ol>
	</div>
</div>

